A brown sofa will tone down the mood in the room to create space for the golden items you want to use. An accent wall in a warmer colour such as red will warm up the space as it creates a focal point. Alternatively, find a wall paper you like, with gold accents to hold the theme together and allow the metallic objects to stand out. Carefully select gold light fittings that match the theme you are going for. Matching chandeliers, table lamps and wall brackets add pomp and style to your space. ALSO READ:

